{"id": "1262710260611940362", "channel_id": "1262710260611940362", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "📜詩歌是她的語言，🌹玫瑰是她的修辭。花園是一道謎題，春天是她的答案。\n西岱的天才詩人少女將帶你回到往昔的玫瑰園，見證於火中誕生的詩篇。\n\n✨奧爾拉登場特典禮包即將釋放，7/16~7/20每日更新奧爾拉的詩篇禮包碼，總計禮包內容為【無垢之芯x100、銀芯x2500】\n\n🎁7/16禮包碼：\n以凋零回答春天\n\n💌禮包內容：\n本日禮包內含：無垢之芯*20、銀芯*500\n\n📍領取時限與條件：\n有效期至2024年8月12日 09:00，守密人≥10級即可領取。\n\n❣️《忘卻前夜》Steam全球願望清單預約已經開啟，歡迎守密人將《忘卻前夜》加入Steam願望清單！「Steam加入願望清單解鎖全服福利」活動進行中！\n⭐Steam商店願望清單連結：https://store.steampowered.com/app/3052450/_/", "timestamp": "2024-07-16T09:59:46.152000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-16T10:29:28.873000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1236951537788649492", "count": 17}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1262710261060599860", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1467931, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1262710260611940362/1262710261060599860/1.jpg?ex=69ccec92&is=69cb9b12&hm=f6a99aa6a70890b189537e66c0ede4ec6c846572c047411f25b1130d4b55e297&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "rich", "title": "Morimens", "url": "https://store.steampowered.com/app/3052450/_/", "description": "\"Morimens\" is a roguelite card-battling game set in a world inspired by the Cthulhu mythos. Within the game, you will connect with a diverse array of awaker, each with distinct personalities, to construct a unique strategic deck tailored to your playstyle. Venture into the misty expanse of the game'"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1262710260611940362", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "🎁奧爾拉登場特典禮包釋放·Ⅰ✨", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181136002664910858"]}
